verbose_text: It was found that compared with those in the empty vector group, the VEGF mRNA level in HTR-8 / SVneo cells was remarkably decreased (* p < 0.05) and the sFlt-1 mRNA level was markedly increased in the silencing group (# p < 0.05) (XREF_FIG), suggesting that decreasing the level of LAMA4 inhibited angiogenesis and induced the occurrence and development of preeclampsia.
